{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-challenges-classic-show-tsx","path":"/learn/front-end-development-libraries/jquery/target-the-same-element-with-multiple-jquery-selectors","result":{"data":{"challengeNode":{"challenge":{"block":"jquery","demoType":null,"title":"Ciljaj na jedan element koristeći više jQuery selektora","description":"<section id=\"description\">\n<p>Sada znate tri načina za ciljanje elemenata: po tipu: <code>$(\"button\")</code>, po klasi objekata: <code>$(\".btn\")</code>, i po identifikatoru <code>$(\"#target1\")</code>.</p>\n<p>Iako je moguće dodati mnogo klasama jednim pozivom od <code>.addClass()</code>, dodajmo ga sa jednim elementom na <em>tri različita načina</em>.</p>\n<p>Ako se oslanjate na <code>.addClass()</code>, dodajte samo jednu klasu u jednom trenutku za jednu funkciju, na tri različita načina:</p>\n<p>Dodaj klasu za <code>animated</code> za sve elemente tipa <code>button</code>.</p>\n<p>Dodaj klasu la <code>shake</code> za sve dugmad sa klasom la <code>.btn</code>.</p>\n<p>Dodajte klasu za <code>btn-primary</code> na dugme sa identifikatorom <code>#target1</code>.</p>\n<p><strong>Napomena:</strong> Treba da se fokusirate samo na jedan element i dodajete samo jednu klasu odjednom. Zajedno, vaši tri selektora će dodati tri klase <code>shake</code>, <code>animated</code>, i <code>btn-primary</code> za <code>#target1</code>.</p>\n</section>","id":"bad87fee1348bd9aed908626","hasEditableBoundaries":false,"instructions":"","notes":null,"challengeType":6,"helpCategory":"JavaScript","videoUrl":null,"superBlock":"front-end-development-libraries","translationPending":false,"forumTopicId":18322,"hooks":null,"fields":{"slug":"/learn/front-end-development-libraries/jquery/target-the-same-element-with-multiple-jquery-selectors"},"required":[{"link":"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/twitter-bootstrap/3.3.7/css/bootstrap.css","src":null},{"link":null,"src":"https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.6.0.min.js"},{"link":"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/animate.css/3.2.0/animate.css","src":null}],"usesMultifileEditor":false,"challengeFiles":[{"fileKey":"indexhtml","ext":"html","name":"index","contents":"<script>\r\n  $(document).ready(function() {\r\n\r\n  });\r\n</script>\r\n\r\n<!-- Only change code above this line -->\r\n\r\n<div class=\"container-fluid\">\r\n  <h3 class=\"text-primary text-center\">jQuery Playground</h3>\r\n  <div class=\"row\">\r\n    <div class=\"col-xs-6\">\r\n      <h4>#left-well</h4>\r\n      <div class=\"well\" id=\"left-well\">\r\n        <button class=\"btn btn-default target\" id=\"target1\">#target1</button>\r\n        <button class=\"btn btn-default target\" id=\"target2\">#target2</button>\r\n        <button class=\"btn btn-default target\" id=\"target3\">#target3</button>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"col-xs-6\">\r\n      <h4>#right-well</h4>\r\n      <div class=\"well\" id=\"right-well\">\r\n        <button class=\"btn btn-default target\" id=\"target4\">#target4</button>\r\n        <button class=\"btn btn-default target\" id=\"target5\">#target5</button>\r\n        <button class=\"btn btn-default target\" id=\"target6\">#target6</button>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n</div>","head":null,"tail":null,"editableRegionBoundaries":[],"history":["index.html"]}],"saveSubmissionToDB":null,"tests":[{"text":"<p>Kod treba da koristi selektor <code>$(\"button\")</code>.</p>","testString":"assert(code.match(/\\$\\s*?\\(\\s*?(?:'|\")\\s*?button\\s*?(?:'|\")/gi));"},{"text":"<p>Vaš kod treba da koristi selector za <code>$(\".btn\")</code>.</p>","testString":"assert(code.match(/\\$\\s*?\\(\\s*?(?:'|\")\\s*?\\.btn\\s*?(?:'|\")/gi));"},{"text":"<p>Vaš kod mora da koristi selektor <code>$(\"#target1\")</code>.</p>","testString":"assert(code.match(/\\$\\s*?\\(\\s*?(?:'|\")\\s*?#target1\\s*?(?:'|\")/gi));"},{"text":"<p>Morate dodati samo jedan kurs/predmet za svaki vaš treći izbor.</p>","testString":"assert(\r\n  code.match(/addClass/g) &&\r\n    code.match(/addClass\\s*?\\(\\s*?('|\")\\s*?[\\w-]+\\s*?\\1\\s*?\\)/g).length > 2\r\n);"},{"text":"<p>Tvoj element za <code>#target1</code> mora imati klase <code>animated</code>, <code>shake</code> i <code>btn-primary</code>.</p>","testString":"assert(\r\n  $('#target1').hasClass('animated') &&\r\n    $('#target1').hasClass('shake') &&\r\n    $('#target1').hasClass('btn-primary')\r\n);"},{"text":"<p>Trebalo bi da koristite jQuery samo za dodavanje ovih klasa elementu.</p>","testString":"assert(!code.match(/class.*animated/g));"}]}}},"pageContext":{"challengeMeta":{"blockHashSlug":"/learn/front-end-development-libraries/#jquery","dashedName":"target-the-same-element-with-multiple-jquery-selectors","certification":"front-end-development-libraries","disableLoopProtectTests":false,"disableLoopProtectPreview":false,"superBlock":"front-end-development-libraries","chapter":null,"module":null,"block":"jquery","isFirstStep":false,"template":null,"required":[{"link":"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/twitter-bootstrap/3.3.7/css/bootstrap.css","src":null},{"link":null,"src":"https://code.jquery.com/jquery-3.6.0.min.js"},{"link":"https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/animate.css/3.2.0/animate.css","src":null}],"isLastChallengeInBlock":false,"nextChallengePath":"/learn/front-end-development-libraries/jquery/remove-classes-from-an-element-with-jquery","prevChallengePath":"/learn/front-end-development-libraries/jquery/delete-your-jquery-functions","id":"bad87fee1348bd9aed908626","saveSubmissionToDB":null},"projectPreview":{"challengeData":{"challengeType":6,"challengeFiles":[{"name":"index","ext":"html","contents":"<script>\r\n  $(document).ready(function() {\r\n    $(\"#target1\").css(\"color\", \"red\");\r\n    $(\"#target1\").prop(\"disabled\", true);\r\n    $(\"#target4\").remove();\r\n    $(\"#target2\").appendTo(\"#right-well\");\r\n    $(\"#target5\").clone().appendTo(\"#left-well\");\r\n    $(\"#target1\").parent().css(\"background-color\", \"red\");\r\n    $(\"#right-well\").children().css(\"color\", \"orange\");\r\n    $(\"#left-well\").children().css(\"color\", \"green\");\r\n    $(\".target:nth-child(2)\").addClass(\"animated bounce\");\r\n    $(\".target:even\").addClass(\"animated shake\");\r\n    $(\"body\").addClass(\"animated hinge\");\r\n  });\r\n</script>\r\n\r\n<!-- Only change code above this line -->\r\n\r\n<div class=\"container-fluid\">\r\n  <h3 class=\"text-primary text-center\">jQuery Playground</h3>\r\n  <div class=\"row\">\r\n    <div class=\"col-xs-6\">\r\n      <h4>#left-well</h4>\r\n      <div class=\"well\" id=\"left-well\">\r\n        <button class=\"btn btn-default target\" id=\"target1\">#target1</button>\r\n        <button class=\"btn btn-default target\" id=\"target2\">#target2</button>\r\n        <button class=\"btn btn-default target\" id=\"target3\">#target3</button>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n    <div class=\"col-xs-6\">\r\n      <h4>#right-well</h4>\r\n      <div class=\"well\" id=\"right-well\">\r\n        <button class=\"btn btn-default target\" id=\"target4\">#target4</button>\r\n        <button class=\"btn btn-default target\" id=\"target5\">#target5</button>\r\n        <button class=\"btn btn-default target\" id=\"target6\">#target6</button>\r\n      </div>\r\n    </div>\r\n  </div>\r\n</div>","history":["index.html"],"fileKey":"indexhtml"}]}},"id":"/learn/front-end-development-libraries/jquery/target-the-same-element-with-multiple-jquery-selectors"}},"staticQueryHashes":["3858520367"],"slicesMap":{}}